                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 item"><i class="fa fa-list icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="name">Can an organisation require me to fill in a particular form?</h3>
                    <p class="description">An organisation might ask you to complete a form in order to simplify their process of collecting the required information. However, the forms are not compulsory to complete if you have provided a valid request to them, and they still
                        have an obligation to respond to your request. This service is designed for the specific purpose so in most cases we do not expect organizations to require any more information other than perhaps to verify your information. If
                        you find you are being required to fill in a form or repeat information that you have already entered via this website please provide this feedback.<br></p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4 item"><i class="fa fa-search icon"></i>
                    <h3 class="name">What if I cannot find the organisation I need?</h3>
                    <p class="description">Please contact us if you are unable to find the organisation you are looking for.<br></p>
                </div>
            </div>
